1
00:00:10,960 --> 00:00:13,420
♪The maple mark on your skin♪

2
00:00:14,230 --> 00:00:17,040
♪The only proof we exist♪

3
00:00:18,210 --> 00:00:21,450
♪I stole you back from destiny♪

4
00:00:21,560 --> 00:00:24,430
♪But can I redeem myself♪

5
00:00:24,430 --> 00:00:26,540
♪I don't care what fate foretells♪

6
00:00:26,750 --> 00:00:30,330
♪Or how rough the road may be♪

7
00:00:30,340 --> 00:00:33,280
♪Stay, I'll fight for you♪

8
00:00:33,610 --> 00:00:37,660
♪That's all I'll ever do♪

9
00:00:37,760 --> 00:00:39,890
♪If life is just a show♪

10
00:00:39,890 --> 00:00:42,650
♪I'll stay with you till the end♪

11
00:00:42,650 --> 00:00:44,980
♪I'm scared we'll wake up alone♪

12
00:00:44,980 --> 00:00:47,960
♪So don't let this dream end♪

13
00:00:47,960 --> 00:00:52,420
♪In my bones, in my heart♪

14
00:00:52,420 --> 00:00:54,100
♪I know I'll have to leave♪

15
00:00:54,100 --> 00:00:55,670
♪You must not leave my side♪

16
00:00:55,670 --> 00:00:57,260
♪No place can hold us in♪

17
00:00:57,260 --> 00:01:01,910
♪Not when it's you and me♪

18
00:01:06,890 --> 00:01:10,400
♪Forever♪

19
00:01:11,490 --> 00:01:15,250
♪In my soul♪

20
00:01:17,260 --> 00:01:23,300
=This Palace Maid Isn't Very Calm=
=Episode 5=

21
00:01:27,680 --> 00:01:28,760
Your Highness.

22
00:01:28,760 --> 00:01:30,560
I brewed this myself.

23
00:01:30,560 --> 00:01:32,710
It's made with smoked plum,
hawthorn, and malt,

24
00:01:32,710 --> 00:01:34,280
with bergamot and mint.

25
00:01:34,400 --> 00:01:36,590
No sugar, but naturally sweet.

26
00:01:36,590 --> 00:01:37,790
Good for digestion

27
00:01:37,790 --> 00:01:38,790
and thirst.

28
00:01:41,430 --> 00:01:42,680
Let me try.

29
00:01:51,350 --> 00:01:52,280
Well?

30
00:01:53,640 --> 00:01:56,120
Much smoother
than the imperial medicine.

31
00:01:57,920 --> 00:01:58,840
Lately,

32
00:01:58,840 --> 00:02:01,400
I couldn't stomach a sip before.

33
00:02:01,760 --> 00:02:04,040
Now my appetite's back.

34
00:02:04,230 --> 00:02:05,350
About the 14th Prince.

35
00:02:05,640 --> 00:02:08,800
I hear he's sleeping better too.

36
00:02:10,360 --> 00:02:11,360
I didn't expect

37
00:02:11,630 --> 00:02:13,000
a young maid

38
00:02:13,280 --> 00:02:14,910
to outshines the physicians.

39
00:02:15,560 --> 00:02:17,360
I dare not take credit.

40
00:02:17,680 --> 00:02:20,710
It's a family recipe.

41
00:02:20,710 --> 00:02:21,840
Your family?

42
00:02:22,080 --> 00:02:23,710
Were they famous doctors?

43
00:02:23,710 --> 00:02:24,840
Not exactly.

44
00:02:25,190 --> 00:02:27,430
Just a medical family,

45
00:02:27,430 --> 00:02:29,710
locally known.

46
00:02:29,840 --> 00:02:32,190
I had some talent,

47
00:02:32,360 --> 00:02:35,120
and studied with my grandfather.

48
00:02:35,120 --> 00:02:35,960
Later,

49
00:02:35,960 --> 00:02:38,710
I read and refined

50
00:02:38,960 --> 00:02:39,870
some old formulas.

51
00:02:39,870 --> 00:02:42,030
That's why they work.

52
00:02:42,240 --> 00:02:43,150
It seems

53
00:02:43,150 --> 00:02:44,680
a woman with a sharp mind

54
00:02:44,910 --> 00:02:46,590
is no less capable than any man.

55
00:02:46,590 --> 00:02:47,440
Mm.

56
00:02:47,470 --> 00:02:48,470
I am pleased

57
00:02:48,560 --> 00:02:49,520
with you.

58
00:02:50,560 --> 00:02:52,080
Keeping you as a regular maid

59
00:02:52,080 --> 00:02:53,120
would be a waste of talent.

60
00:02:53,520 --> 00:02:54,390
Ruizhu.

61
00:02:54,470 --> 00:02:55,520
From today on,

62
00:02:55,800 --> 00:02:58,630
Ye Jin is promoted
to the Private Kitchen.

63
00:02:58,840 --> 00:03:00,680
She is in charge
of all my meals.

64
00:03:01,430 --> 00:03:02,270
Yes.

65
00:03:02,430 --> 00:03:03,270
Your Highness.

66
00:03:06,030 --> 00:03:07,470
Thank you for your grace.

67
00:03:12,240 --> 00:03:13,150
Hello, everyone.

68
00:03:13,800 --> 00:03:16,150
So this is the new favorite.

69
00:03:16,310 --> 00:03:17,630
I wonder what luck she used.

70
00:03:18,080 --> 00:03:19,400
Only a few months in…

71
00:03:19,680 --> 00:03:21,560
The kitchen staff
hasn't changed in decades,

72
00:03:21,910 --> 00:03:23,710
but she just flew straight to the top.

73
00:03:24,590 --> 00:03:26,190
Miss Ye Jin is here.

74
00:03:26,750 --> 00:03:28,190
One bowl of soup

75
00:03:28,190 --> 00:03:30,520
and you won favor?

76
00:03:30,910 --> 00:03:33,240
Being this skilled at your age,

77
00:03:33,960 --> 00:03:35,910
you must be quite a prodigy.

78
00:03:35,910 --> 00:03:38,360
The Empress Dowager
is the only true deity.

79
00:03:38,840 --> 00:03:39,750
We are just

80
00:03:39,960 --> 00:03:42,840
the apprentices making the elixir.

81
00:03:43,680 --> 00:03:45,240
If the elixir works,

82
00:03:45,240 --> 00:03:46,360
everyone is happy.

83
00:03:46,630 --> 00:03:48,630
If it fails,

84
00:03:49,560 --> 00:03:50,910
we're all done.

85
00:03:53,630 --> 00:03:54,470
This is

86
00:03:55,080 --> 00:03:56,520
the new menu.

87
00:03:57,030 --> 00:03:59,800
Her Highness tested it for three days.

88
00:04:00,240 --> 00:04:01,240
Better complexion

89
00:04:01,470 --> 00:04:02,630
and better appetite.

90
00:04:03,240 --> 00:04:04,360
From today,

91
00:04:04,360 --> 00:04:07,870
all meals follow this.

92
00:04:08,240 --> 00:04:09,150
Any changes

93
00:04:09,150 --> 00:04:10,150
and things go wrong,

94
00:04:10,280 --> 00:04:12,800
you'll answer for it.

95
00:04:15,910 --> 00:04:18,070
Quite the authority.

96
00:04:18,360 --> 00:04:20,000
First day here

97
00:04:20,070 --> 00:04:22,310
and already throwing weight around.

98
00:04:23,510 --> 00:04:24,600
Ms. Chun,

99
00:04:24,950 --> 00:04:26,680
you're a veteran.

100
00:04:26,870 --> 00:04:28,560
I'm only new here.

101
00:04:28,560 --> 00:04:30,270
I wouldn't dare challenge you.

102
00:04:30,870 --> 00:04:33,510
But accounts are being audited.

103
00:04:33,510 --> 00:04:35,750
You've handled procurement
for years.

104
00:04:35,750 --> 00:04:38,270
That missing silver?
Enough to retire on.

105
00:04:38,800 --> 00:04:41,310
Even Consort Lan's rewards

106
00:04:41,310 --> 00:04:42,630
are no small amount.

107
00:04:44,630 --> 00:04:46,430
(Tremble, you NPCs.)

108
00:04:46,430 --> 00:04:48,120
(A cheat code player like me)

109
00:04:48,120 --> 00:04:49,600
(can handle you easily.)

110
00:04:55,750 --> 00:04:56,800
Miss Ye Jin.

111
00:04:56,800 --> 00:04:58,720
Ruizhu sent me with a message.

112
00:04:58,960 --> 00:04:59,830
Her Highness will have

113
00:04:59,830 --> 00:05:01,430
Consort Lan and Consort Duan tomorrow

114
00:05:01,430 --> 00:05:02,830
for a meal.

115
00:05:03,270 --> 00:05:05,750
Please get ready

116
00:05:05,750 --> 00:05:07,480
for extra dishes.

117
00:05:07,750 --> 00:05:08,590
Understood.

118
00:05:10,340 --> 00:05:12,140
(Menu)

119
00:05:15,800 --> 00:05:18,000
Those two consorts together?

120
00:05:18,720 --> 00:05:20,270
That's never good news.

121
00:05:20,270 --> 00:05:21,720
It's my first day on the job,

122
00:05:21,720 --> 00:05:23,510
and things are getting intense.

123
00:05:46,190 --> 00:05:47,190
Greetings, Your Highness.

124
00:05:47,430 --> 00:05:48,630
Your Graces.

125
00:06:12,560 --> 00:06:14,480
I hear there's a new chef.

126
00:06:15,070 --> 00:06:17,680
The poria osmanthus cake
is exquisite.

127
00:06:18,070 --> 00:06:19,390
Sweet, fragrant,

128
00:06:19,390 --> 00:06:20,680
and perfectly colored.

129
00:06:24,510 --> 00:06:27,680
But why is it only served to me?

130
00:06:28,600 --> 00:06:29,920
Your Grace,

131
00:06:29,920 --> 00:06:32,270
I knew this was your favorite,

132
00:06:32,270 --> 00:06:34,420
so I made it specifically
for your palate.

133
00:06:34,470 --> 00:06:35,950
That's why
there's only one serving.

134
00:06:36,160 --> 00:06:37,560
How thoughtful.

135
00:06:38,600 --> 00:06:41,920
But pregnant women
have changing tastes.

136
00:06:42,310 --> 00:06:44,800
Why don't you try, Consort Duan?

137
00:06:45,310 --> 00:06:46,680
If she likes it,

138
00:06:46,680 --> 00:06:49,390
you can make more.

139
00:07:15,430 --> 00:07:16,270
Wait.

140
00:07:21,680 --> 00:07:22,870
Pardon me.

141
00:07:23,120 --> 00:07:24,950
There seems to be white specks

142
00:07:24,950 --> 00:07:26,510
on that cake.

143
00:07:26,800 --> 00:07:27,800
I'm afraid

144
00:07:28,270 --> 00:07:30,510
it could be clove powder.

145
00:07:31,120 --> 00:07:33,560
So what if it is?

146
00:07:33,740 --> 00:07:35,040
(Fictional. Do not imitate.)
Your Highness,

147
00:07:35,070 --> 00:07:36,480
clove warms the body

148
00:07:36,600 --> 00:07:38,680
and it's excellent for pastries.

149
00:07:38,870 --> 00:07:39,800
However,

150
00:07:40,000 --> 00:07:41,430
pregnant women should avoid it.

151
00:07:41,750 --> 00:07:43,000
Eating them

152
00:07:43,000 --> 00:07:44,270
can cause abdominal pain

153
00:07:44,270 --> 00:07:46,390
or even a miscarriage.

154
00:07:47,070 --> 00:07:49,680
I couldn't overlook it.

155
00:07:51,310 --> 00:07:52,800
Nonsense.

156
00:07:53,120 --> 00:07:54,390
I've never heard

157
00:07:54,390 --> 00:07:56,160
of it being harmful
to pregnant women.

158
00:07:56,750 --> 00:07:58,070
Suddenly, in your mouth,

159
00:07:58,070 --> 00:08:00,070
it's a deadly poison?

160
00:08:01,190 --> 00:08:03,040
Don't stir trouble

161
00:08:03,240 --> 00:08:04,680
and drive a wedge between us.

162
00:08:10,310 --> 00:08:12,000
Actually…

163
00:08:12,390 --> 00:08:16,190
I'm sensitive to clove.

164
00:08:17,310 --> 00:08:19,680
If not for her warning,

165
00:08:20,240 --> 00:08:21,510
eating that would've

166
00:08:21,830 --> 00:08:22,670
caused more

167
00:08:23,040 --> 00:08:24,870
than just a stomachache.

168
00:08:26,600 --> 00:08:29,430
Who made this?

169
00:08:29,560 --> 00:08:30,630
Forgive me, Your Highness.

170
00:08:30,830 --> 00:08:32,750
I made it.

171
00:08:33,080 --> 00:08:34,360
But I followed

172
00:08:34,360 --> 00:08:35,960
Ye Jin's recipe exactly.

173
00:08:36,150 --> 00:08:37,600
I didn't add anything extra.

174
00:08:37,750 --> 00:08:40,000
Ye Jin runs the kitchen now.

175
00:08:40,510 --> 00:08:42,120
All dishes

176
00:08:42,120 --> 00:08:44,320
are checked by her first.

177
00:08:44,630 --> 00:08:45,720
I just

178
00:08:45,910 --> 00:08:47,440
followed orders.

179
00:08:47,440 --> 00:08:48,720
I don't know

180
00:08:48,720 --> 00:08:50,200
how this happened.

181
00:08:51,080 --> 00:08:51,920
Ye Jin.

182
00:08:52,080 --> 00:08:53,080
Explain.

183
00:08:53,360 --> 00:08:54,360
Your Highness.

184
00:08:54,750 --> 00:08:56,030
When the cakes came out,

185
00:08:56,030 --> 00:08:57,510
I tasted them myself.

186
00:08:57,510 --> 00:08:58,960
They were fine.

187
00:08:59,270 --> 00:09:02,200
The portion on Consort Duan's table

188
00:09:02,200 --> 00:09:03,910
clearly has clove.

189
00:09:04,270 --> 00:09:07,030
It was swapped midway.

190
00:09:07,360 --> 00:09:08,630
In this palace,

191
00:09:08,630 --> 00:09:10,790
accusations aren't enough.

192
00:09:11,360 --> 00:09:13,550
You need proof.

193
00:09:14,360 --> 00:09:16,080
Your Grace.

194
00:09:16,080 --> 00:09:17,390
In my hometown,

195
00:09:17,390 --> 00:09:19,840
food safety is critical.

196
00:09:20,240 --> 00:09:22,030
By the customs,

197
00:09:22,030 --> 00:09:23,630
since I took over the kitchen,

198
00:09:23,630 --> 00:09:25,030
following our practices,

199
00:09:25,030 --> 00:09:27,320
I started a Food Sampling System.

200
00:09:27,510 --> 00:09:28,790
If permitted,

201
00:09:28,790 --> 00:09:30,080
we can bring out the sample dish

202
00:09:30,080 --> 00:09:32,600
and compare it
to the one on Consort Duan's table.

203
00:09:32,600 --> 00:09:33,910
The truth will be clear.

204
00:09:37,150 --> 00:09:37,990
Ruizhu.

205
00:09:38,240 --> 00:09:39,080
Bring it in.

206
00:09:52,550 --> 00:09:53,720
Your Highness, look.

207
00:09:53,720 --> 00:09:55,030
This is the sample cake.

208
00:09:55,030 --> 00:09:56,030
It's yellowish,

209
00:09:56,030 --> 00:09:57,080
soft, and textured.

210
00:10:00,150 --> 00:10:02,630
The one on Consort Duan's table

211
00:10:02,960 --> 00:10:04,750
is pale, white,

212
00:10:05,240 --> 00:10:07,840
and has powder in the cracks.

213
00:10:08,150 --> 00:10:10,510
They clearly didn't come
from the same batch.

214
00:10:13,630 --> 00:10:16,200
Someone did swap them.

215
00:10:17,360 --> 00:10:18,240
Who dares

216
00:10:18,550 --> 00:10:20,910
commit such a foul act

217
00:10:21,080 --> 00:10:22,790
under my nose?

218
00:10:23,320 --> 00:10:24,790
I remember

219
00:10:24,870 --> 00:10:26,960
Ms. Chun was in charge

220
00:10:26,960 --> 00:10:28,720
when the cakes left the kitchen.

221
00:10:29,080 --> 00:10:31,480
Unless she was negligent,

222
00:10:31,480 --> 00:10:33,750
or someone ordered her to do it,

223
00:10:33,750 --> 00:10:34,960
no one would've dared

224
00:10:35,320 --> 00:10:36,870
to swap them.

225
00:10:38,440 --> 00:10:39,320
Mercy, Your Highness.

226
00:10:39,370 --> 00:10:40,220
But I'm…

227
00:10:40,240 --> 00:10:41,270
I'm innocent.

228
00:10:41,400 --> 00:10:42,240
Guards.

229
00:10:42,360 --> 00:10:43,240
Take Chun

230
00:10:43,360 --> 00:10:45,840
to the Department of Justice
and interrogate thoroughly.

231
00:10:46,080 --> 00:10:48,600
I want the truth.

232
00:10:48,700 --> 00:10:49,550
Your Highness.

233
00:10:49,670 --> 00:10:50,790
I'm innocent.

234
00:10:50,790 --> 00:10:51,630
Your Highness.

235
00:10:52,120 --> 00:10:53,120
Your Highness.

236
00:10:54,720 --> 00:10:55,560
Ye Jin.

237
00:10:56,030 --> 00:10:57,440
Your food sampling

238
00:10:57,720 --> 00:10:59,320
and sealing methods

239
00:10:59,600 --> 00:11:00,910
very sound.

240
00:11:01,120 --> 00:11:02,120
The palace is

241
00:11:02,360 --> 00:11:03,390
a complex place.

242
00:11:03,750 --> 00:11:05,720
Food is vital here.

243
00:11:06,080 --> 00:11:07,550
From now on,

244
00:11:07,790 --> 00:11:09,080
follow her rules.

245
00:11:09,600 --> 00:11:10,910
Seal and store

246
00:11:11,080 --> 00:11:12,670
all dishes

247
00:11:12,790 --> 00:11:13,960
for three days.

248
00:11:14,270 --> 00:11:15,390
Track all

249
00:11:15,960 --> 00:11:17,270
kitchen access.

250
00:11:17,550 --> 00:11:18,480
Any mistake

251
00:11:18,790 --> 00:11:19,960
must be investigated.

252
00:11:20,390 --> 00:11:21,230
Yes.

253
00:11:21,600 --> 00:11:22,870
Your Highness, you're wise.

254
00:11:23,870 --> 00:11:25,600
If we had done this sooner,

255
00:11:26,390 --> 00:11:27,870
no one

256
00:11:28,320 --> 00:11:29,320
would have

257
00:11:29,910 --> 00:11:31,480
had a chance.

258
00:11:39,630 --> 00:11:41,000
Greetings, Your Grace.

259
00:11:46,360 --> 00:11:47,960
Greetings, Your Grace.

260
00:11:53,150 --> 00:11:54,670
So you're Ye Jin.

261
00:11:55,320 --> 00:11:57,000
Quite capable.

262
00:11:57,240 --> 00:12:00,150
Days ago, a prisoner.

263
00:12:00,630 --> 00:12:02,030
Now you're

264
00:12:02,200 --> 00:12:04,440
the Empress Dowager's favorite.

265
00:12:04,870 --> 00:12:07,480
Even a twenty-year veteran like Chun

266
00:12:07,480 --> 00:12:08,840
fell to you.

267
00:12:09,150 --> 00:12:10,670
Do you know

268
00:12:11,030 --> 00:12:12,030
what happens

269
00:12:12,030 --> 00:12:13,750
to those

270
00:12:14,200 --> 00:12:15,670
who oppose me?

271
00:12:16,150 --> 00:12:17,960
I only do my duty.

272
00:12:17,960 --> 00:12:19,390
No intent to oppose.

273
00:12:19,870 --> 00:12:20,710
Really?

274
00:12:21,630 --> 00:12:22,790
Pardon me.

275
00:12:23,480 --> 00:12:24,840
Have you

276
00:12:24,910 --> 00:12:26,790
been feeling lower abdominal pain?

277
00:12:27,240 --> 00:12:28,600
Hot and cold at night?

278
00:12:28,600 --> 00:12:29,840
Sharp pain, poor sleep?

279
00:12:29,910 --> 00:12:32,000
Bloating after eating,

280
00:12:32,440 --> 00:12:35,480
cramps when not?

281
00:12:36,360 --> 00:12:37,440
What are you implying?

282
00:12:37,510 --> 00:12:39,120
I know a bit of medicine.

283
00:12:39,320 --> 00:12:40,440
Specifically women's health.

284
00:12:41,000 --> 00:12:43,270
Pale complexion,

285
00:12:43,270 --> 00:12:44,510
dry lips, weak qi,

286
00:12:44,510 --> 00:12:45,790
red veins in your eyes.

287
00:12:45,870 --> 00:12:48,030
Classic blood stasis and uterine cold.

288
00:12:48,210 --> 00:12:49,410
It's a stubborn condition

289
00:12:49,480 --> 00:12:50,390
that's hard to cure

290
00:12:50,390 --> 00:12:51,320
and easy to relapse.

291
00:12:51,840 --> 00:12:54,270
I'm sure you've seen physicians.

292
00:12:54,720 --> 00:12:55,840
But they are men.

293
00:12:56,480 --> 00:12:58,000
They are too cautious

294
00:12:58,000 --> 00:12:59,600
to examine fully.

295
00:12:59,960 --> 00:13:01,870
They only give you mild tonics

296
00:13:01,870 --> 00:13:02,910
for temporary relief,

297
00:13:02,910 --> 00:13:03,960
but don't fix the problem.

298
00:13:04,480 --> 00:13:05,390
But,

299
00:13:06,630 --> 00:13:07,960
I can cure it.

300
00:13:15,360 --> 00:13:16,360
Rise.

301
00:13:17,790 --> 00:13:18,780
Thank you, Your Grace.

302
00:13:19,960 --> 00:13:21,870
Bold words

303
00:13:22,240 --> 00:13:23,910
for a maid.

304
00:13:24,120 --> 00:13:25,510
I wouldn't dare lie.

305
00:13:25,720 --> 00:13:28,030
I only noticed something unusual

306
00:13:28,120 --> 00:13:29,510
and feared delaying your treatment.

307
00:13:29,910 --> 00:13:31,320
If untreated,

308
00:13:31,320 --> 00:13:32,510
it will damage your qi

309
00:13:32,510 --> 00:13:33,440
and harm your fertility.

310
00:13:34,120 --> 00:13:36,840
Even if you regain the Emperor's favor,

311
00:13:37,790 --> 00:13:40,080
it'll be hard to carry a child to term.

312
00:13:42,270 --> 00:13:43,110
Your Grace.

313
00:13:43,150 --> 00:13:45,050
I remember three months ago,

314
00:13:45,050 --> 00:13:46,910
you had night pain
and called for a physician.

315
00:13:46,910 --> 00:13:48,630
He said it was cold invasion.

316
00:13:49,030 --> 00:13:51,480
But the meds didn't work.

317
00:13:52,910 --> 00:13:54,240
Then what

318
00:13:54,960 --> 00:13:56,720
do you suggest?

319
00:13:57,000 --> 00:14:00,000
Daily moxa with mugwort and motherwort.

320
00:14:00,200 --> 00:14:03,480
Warm compress on key points.

321
00:14:03,720 --> 00:14:05,120
(Fictional. Do not imitate.)
The pain will fade in three days.

322
00:14:05,120 --> 00:14:06,790
You'll see results in seven.

323
00:14:07,000 --> 00:14:08,790
This method clears the meridians

324
00:14:08,790 --> 00:14:10,390
without hurting your energy.

325
00:14:10,510 --> 00:14:12,320
If Your Grace trusts me,

326
00:14:12,370 --> 00:14:13,630
you may as well use this method

327
00:14:13,750 --> 00:14:14,790
and give it a try.

328
00:14:23,280 --> 00:14:25,720
♪I am but an outsider♪

329
00:14:25,760 --> 00:14:27,920
♪Yet something drags me deeper♪

330
00:14:28,160 --> 00:14:32,200
♪Outwit the world but not the way we meet♪

331
00:14:32,200 --> 00:14:36,440
♪Splendid blooms line deadly ground♪

332
00:14:40,720 --> 00:14:43,960
♪Life's a phantom, yet I find you♪

333
00:14:44,120 --> 00:14:47,520
♪In a world of lies, you're all that's clear♪

334
00:14:47,520 --> 00:14:50,040
♪I know how this story ends♪

335
00:14:50,040 --> 00:14:54,600
♪I still want what's in your eyes♪

336
00:14:54,920 --> 00:14:59,040
♪Truth or lie—I can't tell♪

337
00:15:04,000 --> 00:15:07,320
♪You hide it all behind your lines♪

338
00:15:07,320 --> 00:15:10,600
♪So familiar, yet out of reach♪

339
00:15:10,800 --> 00:15:13,880
♪A history that no one can search♪

340
00:15:14,120 --> 00:15:17,400
♪Like you drift in from another star♪

341
00:15:17,440 --> 00:15:19,200
♪I am but an outsider♪

342
00:15:19,200 --> 00:15:21,440
♪Yet something drags me deeper♪

343
00:15:21,440 --> 00:15:25,480
♪Outwit the world but not the way we meet♪

344
00:15:25,480 --> 00:15:30,160
♪Splendid blooms line deadly ground♪

345
00:15:34,080 --> 00:15:37,480
♪Life's a phantom, yet I find you♪

346
00:15:37,480 --> 00:15:40,840
♪In a world of lies, you're all that's clear♪

347
00:15:40,840 --> 00:15:43,320
♪I know how this story ends♪

348
00:15:43,320 --> 00:15:47,480
♪I still want what's in your eyes♪

349
00:15:47,480 --> 00:15:50,760
♪When it's over and I'm gone♪

350
00:15:50,760 --> 00:15:54,560
♪Please forget me and move on♪

351
00:15:54,560 --> 00:16:00,800
♪Just let this absurd dream fade♪

352
00:16:03,960 --> 00:16:12,320
♪Snow hides our tracks♪

353
00:16:15,880 --> 00:16:25,600
♪When do I finally wake♪
